---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import { siteName, siteDescription } from '@/lib/constants'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
import Navbar from '@/components/Navbar.astro'
import KhaledComponent from '@/components/KhaledComponent.astro'
const title = `About ${siteName}`
const description = siteDescription
---

<style>
  .getStarted {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 2.5em;
    letter-spacing: 0.5pt;
    padding: 0.5em;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 350px;
    border: solid 1px;
    text-align: center;
    border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
    border-left-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 5px 1px rgb(0, 0, 0);
    transition: 0.1s linear;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);
    background-image: radial-gradient(
      311px at 38% -1%,
      rgb(87 121 79) 0%,
      rgb(99 143 74) 5%,
      rgb(48 96 31) 48%,
      rgb(12 41 10) 67%,
      rgb(55 55 55) 83%,
      rgb(54 136 50) 92%,
      rgb(24 199 54) 98%,
      rgb(94 203 46) 99%,
      rgb(69 255 0) 100%
    );
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .getStarted:hover {
    background-image: radial-gradient(
      311px at 38% -1%,
      rgb(126 174 115) 0%,
      rgb(123, 175, 93) 5%,
      rgb(62, 123, 42) 48%,
      rgb(28, 123, 19) 67%,
      rgb(85, 123, 58) 83%,
      rgb(84, 154, 80) 92%,
      rgb(95, 177, 109) 98%,
      rgb(123, 181, 97) 99%,
      rgb(123, 185, 100) 100%
    );
  }

  .getStarted:active {
    background-image: radial-gradient(
      311px at 38% -1%,
      rgb(87 121 79) 0%,
      rgb(99 143 74) 5%,
      rgb(48 96 31) 48%,
      rgb(12 41 10) 67%,
      rgb(55 55 55) 83%,
      rgb(54 136 50) 92%,
      rgb(24 199 54) 98%,
      rgb(94 203 46) 99%,
      rgb(69 255 0) 100%
    );
    cursor: pointer;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 1px 1px rgb(0, 0, 0);
  }
</style>

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Navbar active={'/about'} />
  <div class="p-4 sm:p-8 max-w-screen-xl m-auto">
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-8">
      <div class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lg p-5 mt-16 card">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-2">Et Tu, Bro?</h1>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Like most bros, we struggled finding <strong>high quality, affordable products.</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Lost in a daze of mass-produced garbage and overpriced caske re-defining opulence, we knew
          there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          Have you ever just wanted to find the best overall product in a genre, without wading
          through over-opinionated troll-spew?
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">Do you struggle finding good gifts for your significant (br)other?</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Look no further..</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Good stuff, for good bros.</p>
        <p class="mt-4">Welcome to <strong>Cool Toy, Bro! üòé</strong></p>
        <div class="p-4 mt-4 text-center">
          <div id="getStarted" class="getStarted">üü¢ Get Started</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-lg p-5 sm:mt-16 card">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-bold">How does it work?</h2>
        <p class="mt-4">
          For some links, we will recieve a small reward, should you decide to purchase a product.
          For others, we simply track whether or not you showed interest from us; nothing more. If
          you do decide to click one of the buy buttons on this site, seriously, bless up üôèüôå
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          I'm just a bro trying to break out of the matrix, and every one of your clicks gets me
          closer to that goal.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4">
          In reward, we offer you this DJ Khaled random quote generator, which is actively
          maintained. Enjoy more life, more success, more blessings, and more keys to success.
        </p>
        <!-- <p class="mt-4">
          You can also <a href="/donate" class="underline">donate to the cause</a> if you feel compelled.
        </p> -->
        <p class="mt-4">
          For everything else, email <span class="underline">support@cooltoybro.com</span>
          and I'll get back to you as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <br />
        <KhaledComponent />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<script>
  // https://docs.astro.build/en/guides/view-transitions/#astropage-load
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => {
    document.getElementById('getStarted')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      if (window.innerWidth >= 768) {
        window.location.pathname = '/all'
      } else {
        document.querySelector('#hamburger.')?.click()
      }
    })
  })
</script>
